
sample_edwards_curve: Edwards curves sample

Sample includes eddsa and rfc7748 for curve 25519 and 448.

To run (load and start) container:
$ mwtest.py -c100 run sample_edwards_curve.img

To send data to container:
$ cmtest data -f100 "Sign me please"

To unload container:
$ mwtest.py -c100 unload
